<TEXT>
<P>
 Congratulations to the Rams for conducting a shrewd 1994 draft. Instead of 
taking a future franchise quarterback to lead them over the next 10-15 years, 
the Ram brain trust concurred that any quarterback, even Chris Miller on 
crutches, can hand off to Jerome Bettis in the Ground Chuck offense. 
</P>
