COLLEGE ROUNDUP; QUINLAN LIFTS MASTER'S TO 12-11 VICTORY OVER BIOLA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Mike Quinlan's pinch-hit, two-run home run with one out in the bottom of the 
ninth inning lifted The Master's College to a 12-11 nonconference baseball 
victory over Biola on Friday in Newhall. 
</P>
<P>
 Mark Balch (1-6) got his first victory despite allowing nine earned runs while 
going the distance for the Mustangs (13-30-2). SOFTBALL 
</P>
<P>
 CS Northridge -- The Matadors' Western Athletic Conference doubleheader 
against Colorado State at Fort Collins, Colo., was snowed out and will not be 
made up. 
