</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The deadline for the fifth annual Writer's Film Project has been extended to 
May 17. A yearlong program sponsored by Amblin Entertainment and Universal 
Pictures, it offers fiction, theater and film writers the opportunity to begin 
a career in screenwriting. Information: (818) 777-0998. 
