<P>
 Sunny Sunrise, seeking a second consecutive victory in the 1 1/8-mile race, 
was three lengths ahead of third-place Compadre. 
</P>
<P>
 Returning to the scene of his victory in the 1992 Blue Grass Stakes, Pistols 
And Roses was timed in 1:51 3/5 under Mike Smith. 
