<TEXT>
<P>
 Campaign funds -- An addition error by the office of Assemblywoman Diane 
Martinez (D-Rosemead) caused Common Cause to rank Martinez as the top 1993 
campaign fund raiser among Assembly freshmen, as reported in The Times. She 
actually raised $41,784 instead of $262,252. Martinez's office said it 
over-reported what she raised in 1993 by adding funds that were received in 
previous years. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Correction 
</P>
</TYPE>
